------------------------------------------\\nCOMMENT ON TABLE strategies IS \'Tr
ading strategy definitions and configuration\';\\nCOMMENT ON TABLE strategy_sign
als IS \'Trading signals generated by strategies\';\\nCOMMENT ON TABLE strategy_
positions IS \'Position attribution to strategies\';\\nCOMMENT ON TABLE strategy
_trades IS \'Trade attribution to strategies for P&L tracking\';\\nCOMMENT ON TA
BLE strategy_performance IS \'Time-series performance metrics per strategy\';\\n
COMMENT ON TABLE strategy_runs IS \'Log of strategy execution runs\';\\n", "mode
