empts: 3,\\n  retryDelayMs: 5000,\\n  cwd: optionalWorkingDirectory, // for Pyth
on scripts\\n}\\n```\\n\\n## Cron Alternative\\n\\nIf you prefer cron, use these
entries:\\n\\n```cron\\n# Market data every 5 minutes\\n*/5 * * * * cd /path/to/
