thon"\n  intervalMs: 5 * 60 * 1000, // 5 minutes\n  retryAttempts: 3,\n  retryDe
layMs: 5000,\n  cwd: optionalWorkingDirectory, // for Python scripts\n}\n```\n\n
## Cron Alternative\n\nIf you prefer cron, use these entries:\n\n```cron\n# Mark
et data every 5 minutes\n*/5 * * * * cd /path/to/backend && node pipeline/fetch_
